362
00:26:47,210 --> 00:26:50,550
Dia selalu bersamanya seperti debu.

363
00:26:52,250 --> 00:26:54,149
Sekarang akhirnya, dia akan terlihat.

364
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,329
Karena bunganya telah bermekaran,

365
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:07,869
